(1062, '火宅', '', 'film', 1979, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/116184.jpg', '', 116184, 'tt1238114', 'null', 'Through puppets and animation, a traveler tells his story of walking through Settsu, coming to the town of Ikuta. He asks if someone can show him the Seeker\'s Mound. Late that day, a solitary maiden says she will lead him there.', 1140, '0.00', 0, 'Animation,Drame'),
(1063, 'House of Forbidden Secrets', '', 'film', 2013, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/33526.jpg', '', 33526, 'tt2630310', 'null', 'Jacob Hunt has had some very bad breaks in life. His wife left him, his friends have all abandoned him, and his children barely see him! Jacob has been given an amazing gift and the chance he needs to get back on his feet and start anew. Jacob has landed the job of overnight security officer at the old ShadowView Manor. It has now been turned into a commercial office and retail building. Jacob is about to learn nights around the old Manor contains many secrets. A dark past that is breaking through the boundaries of time, leaking into this dimension. As luck would have it, Jacob\'s first night on the job is the anniversary of a dark tragedy that has stained the building.', 5880, '0.00', 0, 'Horreur'),
(1064, 'メゾン・ド・ヒミコ', '', 'film', 2005, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/118773.jpg', '', 118773, 'tt0451123', '6xWtBAD7tEA', 'Saori is a young woman struggling to make her way in life. Her gay father, Himiko, had abandoned Saori and her mother years before. Now her father\'s young lover Haruhiko shows up to tell Saori that her father is dying of cancer. Still angry with her father but in need of money, Saori travels to the House of Himiko, a nursing home established by her father for gay men. Over time, a tenuous relationship begins to develop between Saori, her father, and Haruhiko.', 7800, '0.00', 0, 'Drame'),
(1065, 'House of Last Things', '', 'film', 2013, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/51483.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/51483.jpg', 51483, 'tt1464539', 'BNI8KCMBRUQ', 'A mind-bending thriller set in Portland, Oregon about an unspoken tragedy and its effects on a house, its temporary caretakers and the owners, a classical music critic and his wife on a recuperative trip to Italy.', 6600, '2.00', 1, 'Fantastique,Thriller'),
(1066, '嚦咕嚦咕對對碰', '', 'film', 2007, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/109500.jpg', '', 109500, 'tt0934895', 'null', 'Gi, who wants to start up her business in Fu Gui Mall, needs to learn to play Taiwan mahjong to be part of the tenants there. All the other tenants teach her the techniques of the game but Fu Ho defeats Gi. However, he is impressed with her determination and rents a place to Gi. Meanwhile, Fu Ho\'s son, Sun Gui, returns to Hong Kong and is planning to take over the mall. He finds four mahjong experts to gamble with the tenants. Gi, Sam, Lam and the others lose their money and means of survival. Luckily, Lam finds', 5400, '0.00', 0, 'Comédie'),
(1067, 'পারমিতার এক দিন', '', 'film', 2000, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/42645.jpg', '', 42645, 'tt0249866', 'null', 'Sanaka and Paromita are mother and daughter-in-law who, despite differences in age, backgrounds and temperaments, build a strong bond together. However when Paromita has a failed marriage and leaves the house, Sanaka is heartbroken.', 7800, '4.00', 1, 'Drame'),
(1068, 'House of Mortal Sin', '', 'film', 1976, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/55583.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/55583.jpg', 55583, 'tt0072813', 'Ni8cHAng0Rw', 'Après sa rencontre avec un ancien camarade, Bernard Cutler qui a trouvé un travail dans une église, Jenny Welch se dispute avec son petit ami.  Histoire de parler à quelqu\'un, elle se rend dans l\'église où officie Bernard. Malheureusement, ce ne sera pas Bernard qui la recevra dans le confessionnal.', 6240, '0.00', 0, 'Horreur'),
(1069, 'නොමියෙන මතකය', '', 'film', 2018, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/86985.jpg', '', 86985, 'tt6151592', 'zGmNeVLOxtY', 'A surreal and disturbing tale centred on two divided villages in a civil war where women are unable to conceive and a remedy is desperately sought.', 5700, '0.00', 0, 'Drame'),
(1070, 'House of Pride – Ballroom Boudoir', '', 'film', 2021, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/95370.jpg', '', 95370, '', 'null', 'Montreal artistic collective House of Pride takes you behind the scenes of innovative performances in drag, dance and the performing arts. A queer film that plays with gender in a provocative, avant-garde, innovative and legendary way while celebrating female power!', 240, '0.00', 0, 'Documentaire'),
(1071, 'House Of Quarantine', '', 'film', 2021, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/91380.jpg', '', 91380, 'tt12440242', 'YycAS407HaE', 'Nine people have been locked down together in a house while trying to make a movie. Unknowingly, one of their group has COVID-19, which leads to a desperate battle for survival.', 4860, '0.00', 0, 'Thriller'),
(1072, 'House of Ra: The Legend of Reo', '', 'film', 2023, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/107769.jpg', '', 107769, 'tt12861792', 'null', 'On National Reo Day, The Sol Elder sits down to talk about the Legend behind Reo of the House of Ra. There was a prophecy that a fallen house will regain glory by finding an ancient life source which will replenish the scarce resources to the planet for eternity. A young girl and the sole member of the House of Ra finds a relic that will lead her to the Great life Star. She embarks on a journey with a few friends to reclaim and rebuild her house honor by saving the planet.', 0, '0.00', 0, 'Aventure,Science-fiction,Fantastique'),
(1073, 'House Of Salem', '', 'film', 2016, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/80485.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/80485.jpg', 80485, 'tt5122092', 'kyCTAzGrPLY', 'Kidnappers become a child\'s unlikely protectors when demonic forces attack their safe house, emerging from the walls in search of human sacrifice.', 6000, '0.00', 0, 'Horreur'),
(1074, 'House Of Secrets', 'Divorce sous surveillance', 'film', 2014, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/20015.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/20015.jpg', 20015, 'tt3159738', 'null', 'Le divorce de Sam Manning et de Julie Holt vient d\'être prononcé. Chacun a droit à la moitié de la maison de Beverly Hills qu\'ils viennent d\'acheter. Julie n\'en veut pas, mais Sam insiste pour la lui laisser. Elle y emménage dans l\'idée de terminer les travaux et de la vendre au plus vite. En faisant ses courses, elle rencontre Tyler Jordan, un homme à tout faire qui vient terminer les travaux chez elle. Julie et Tyler deviennent vite très proches, mais commence même à se méfier de Tyler après la disparition d\'un de ses colliers et demande à son amie Alison, l\'avocate qui s\'est occupée de son divorce, de faire mener une enquête sur le passé de Tyler.', 5040, '4.00', 1, 'Téléfilm,Thriller,Drame,Mystère'),
(1075, 'House of Series', '', 'film', 2020, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/91326.jpg', '', 91326, '', 'null', 'La Maison Blanche et ses occupants fascinent et constituent une manne inépuisable d\'histoires pour les créateurs : comédies ou thriller, drame ou soap, tout fonctionne. Mais pourquoi inspirent-ils tellement la fiction et plaisent-ils autant au public ? Ces séries politiques participent-elles au mythe américain ? \"House of Series\"\" plonge dans les coulisses du pouvoir américain et notamment l\'univers de la fiction politique.', 3060, '5.00', 1, 'Documentaire'),
(1076, 'House Of Shakira: Live At Firefest 2005', '', 'film', 2006, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/89678.jpg', '', 89678, '', 'null', '', 0, '0.00', 0, 'Musique'),
(1077, '眠れる美女', '', 'film', 1995, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/83121.jpg', '', 83121, 'tt0190581', 'null', 'About an establishment where old men pay to sleep besides young girls that had been narcotized and happen to be naked, the sleeping beauties. The old men are expected to take sleeping pills and share the bed for a whole night with a girl without attempting anything of bad taste like putting a finger inside their mouths.', 6600, '0.00', 0, 'Drame'),
(1078, 'House of Strangers', 'La Maison des étrangers', 'film', 1949, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/72620.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/72620.jpg', 72620, 'tt0041487', 'M7gDQZE_CYQ', 'Reglements de comptes, haine et passion dans une famille de la Petite Italie de New York. Max Monetti, brillant avocat a ete envoye en prison sur la denonciation d\'un de ses freres jaloux de l\'affection que lui portait leur pere, modeste coiffeur devenu banquier. A sa sortie, malgre l\'amour d\'Irene qui le supplie de partir, il est bien decide a se venger.', 6060, '3.67', 3, 'Crime,Drame'),
(1079, '一樓1鬼', '', 'film', 2007, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/43366.jpg', '', 43366, 'tt9609716', 'null', 'The inhabitants of a decrepit inner-city tenement building are terrified to discover that the malevolent spirit of a former tenant has been summoned when one of the current residents broke an unspoken vow. Now, as demolition day draws near, the enraged entity sets out to cause as much mischief as possible before the wrecking ball strikes.', 5400, '0.00', 0, 'Horreur'),
(1080, 'House of the Living Dead', '', 'film', 1974, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/50503.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/50503.jpg', 50503, 'tt0070198', 'null', 'Dans une plantation sud-africaine, un maniaque est en liberté, tuant d\'abord les animaux du domaine, puis en commençant par les membres humains.', 5220, '0.00', 0, 'Science-fiction,Horreur'),
(1081, 'House of the Long Shadows', 'Le Manoir de la peur', 'film', 1983, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/86428.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/86428.jpg', 86428, 'tt0085693', '8UP8A1LtChw', 'Un écrivain américain se rend dans un manoir isolé du Pays de Galle après avoir parié 20 000$ qu\'il pourrait écrire un grand roman tel que \"Les Hauts de Hurlevent\" en 24 h. Cependant, à son arrivée, il découvre que le manoir est loin d\'être inhabité.', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Horreur,Comédie,Mystère'),
(1082, 'House of Time', '', 'film', 2016, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/30015.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/30015.jpg', 30015, 'tt3772660', 'iqA3nwMYLXk', 'Robert d\'Eglantine invite ses amis à passer quelques jours dans une vieille maison de campagne où il leur propose de se lancer dans une aventure audacieuse à la destination surprenante.', 5040, '4.00', 5, 'Comédie,Science-fiction,Thriller'),
(1083, '沖霄樓', '', 'film', 1982, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/76390.jpg', '', 76390, 'tt0082174', 'D7g-eCQpoU0', 'It all started with The Five Venoms, the internationally loved kung-fu thriller. It continued through more than a dozen bloody good entertainments featuring the same actors in different roles. This is considered the last official \"Venoms\" movie, but what a film it is. There\'s one plasma-spurting attack after another as heroes and rogues alike try to solve the secrets of this hell house. The core Venoms themselves choreograph the gory fun in this fond farewell to their worldwide film series sensation!', 5700, '0.00', 0, 'Action'),
