(1191, 'A Dog\'s Breakfast', 'Mon beauf, ma sœur et moi', 'film', 2007, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/3932.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/3932.jpg', 3932, 'tt0796314', 'wmN6u8iYFlI', 'Patrick et Marilyn, frère et sœur, entretiennent depuis toujours une relation très explosive et conflictuelle. Pas étonnant donc, de voir une guerre déclarer lorsque Marilyn ramène chez elle Ryan, une star de la TV, qui n\'est autre que son fiancé.', 5280, '4.11', 9, 'Comédie,Horreur'),
(1192, '佐藤家の朝食、鈴木家の夕食', '', 'film', 2013, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/112396.jpg', '', 112396, 'tt14202642', 'null', 'High school student Takumi lives with his two mothers in a beautiful house in Tokyo. Moving into a house across the street is Sora and her two fathers. One day Takumi and Sora begin a quest to seek answers long hidden and silent in their unconventional families. Takumi sets out to determine the identity of his father, and Sora devises a plan to integrate herself fully into her family. The ordeals of these households stretch the traditional notions of family, convention and tradition.', 6120, '0.00', 0, 'Drame'),
(1193, 'Breakfast for Two', 'Déjeuner pour deux', 'film', 1937, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/109223.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/109223.jpg', 109223, 'tt0028659', 'null', 'Une belle et riche héritière du Texas fait la connaissance d\'un play-boy non moins opulent. Tous deux se plaisent mais ne peuvent se l\'avouer : car si elle a le coeur libre, lui, par contre, est déjà promis à une autre. Les voilà, semble-t-il, condamnés à échanger sourires et taquineries en attendant l\'inévitable séparation. Mais il ne faut jamais désespérer. Tout pourrait très vite changer si le jeune homme se décidait à ouvrir les yeux. Il découvrirait que sa fiancée chérie n\'a en fait qu\'une idée en tête : se remplir les poches à ses dépens...', 4020, '0.00', 0, 'Comédie,Romance'),
(1194, 'Breakfast with Scot', '', 'film', 2007, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/63681.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/63681.jpg', 63681, 'tt0910847', 'KDO6ImFasS0', 'Eric, un ancien joueur des Maple Leafs de Toronto est devenu commentateur sportif et mène une existence rangée auprès de Sam, son compagnon. Mais l\'univers du couple bascule rapidement quand Eric doit s\'occuper de son neveu Scot âgé de 11 ans, et dont la mère vient de mourir. Si Sam est ravi de devenir père de substitution, Eric ne l\'est pas...', 5700, '4.00', 4, 'Comédie,Drame'),
(1195, 'Pressed', 'Hit Fast', 'film', 2011, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/15214.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/15214.jpg', 15214, 'tt1716759', 'rX7cUDwRbAY', 'Sans emplois, Jesse et Sam errent en voiture et attendent la bonne occasion pour s\'en mettre plein les poches. Tout s\'accélère lorsqu\'une mallette pleine de billets est déposée à l\'arrière de leur véhicule. Occupés à tout dépenser, ils ignorent que l\'argent appartient à un trafiquant de drogue bien décidé à le récupérer...', 5700, '2.00', 5, 'Crime,Thriller'),
(1196, 'The World\'s Fastest Indian', 'Burt Munro', 'film', 2005, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/11480.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/11480.jpg', 11480, 'tt0412080', '02Yy1vihIKs', 'Nouvelle Zélande, fin des années 60. A 65 ans passés, Burt Munro, passionné de moto, n\'a qu\'une idée en tête : participer à la prestigieuse course de Bonneville dans l\'Utah. Il réussit à financer son voyage, et prend la route pour les Etats-Unis avec sa vieille moto \"Indian\" bricolée par ses soins...', 7560, '4.20', 35, 'Drame,Aventure,Histoire'),
(1197, 'Tom and Jerry: The Fast and the Furry', 'Tom et Jerry : La course de l’année', 'film', 2005, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/60285.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/60285.jpg', 60285, 'tt0487176', 'In5DCUeumFY', 'Tom et Jerry participent à une compétition automobile intense appelée la « super course » dans le but de gagner le grand prix: un manoir luxueux ! Au volant de voitures surpuissantes se déplaçant au sol, sur l\'eau et même dans les airs, ils découvrent les point d\'intérêts de différents endroits du monde dans cette compétition effrénée, semant le désordre au passage.', 4260, '3.56', 9, 'Familial,Animation,Comédie,Action,Aventure'),
(1198, 'A Faster Horse', '', 'film', 2015, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/32396.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/32396.jpg', 32396, 'tt3762974', 'rWPjtIQOU84', 'David Gelb (Jiro Dreams of Sushi) tackles another venerable, beloved, and long-standing institution: the Mustang, crown jewel of the Ford fleet. Only this institution is in turmoil. As the fiftieth anniversary of the Mustang approaches and the car industry struggles through the deepest trough of the financial crisis, Ford launches a redesign. Now the jobs of workers at Ford’s Flat Rock Assembly Plant, the expectations of the thousands of Mustang devotees, and the livelihood of the city of Detroit are all placed squarely on the shoulders of Dave Pericak. As chief program engineer, he will guide the 2015 Mustang from assembly floor to showroom—if only he can get that vibration out of the steering wheel.', 5400, '3.80', 5, 'Documentaire'),
(1199, 'Animals, Whores ', '', 'film', 2010, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/22886.jpg', '', 22886, 'tt4122714', 'JJBYD4H5F1I', 'Animals, Whores ', 0, '0.00', 0, 'Documentaire'),
(1200, 'Bed and Breakfast', '', 'film', 1930, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/54067.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/54067.jpg', 54067, 'tt0020676', 'null', 'A newlywed couple have a fight, and in order to get even with one another, each decides to take up with a lover but without actually going through with \"the deed\".', 4080, '0.00', 0, 'Comédie'),
(1201, 'Bed ', '', 'film', 2010, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/65837.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/65837.jpg', 65837, 'tt1678040', 'Zv1YhfhXETA', 'Bed and Breakfast is a romantic comedy about a saleswoman from a large department store in Rio who discovers she has inherited property in the wine country of California. She could never expect what she would find in \"Webster\", a small country town', 5340, '0.00', 0, 'Comédie,Romance'),
(1202, 'Belfast, exercices de sauvetage', '', 'film', 1897, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/63359.jpg', '', 63359, 'tt2034627', 'null', 'Belfast firefighters demonstrate a ladder.', 60, '0.00', 0, 'Documentaire'),
(1203, 'Bigger Stronger Faster*', 'Bigger, Stronger, Faster*', 'film', 2008, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/22014.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/22014.jpg', 22014, 'tt1151309', '3KzGfuFFSxA', 'Quand vous découvrez que vos héros ont tous brisé les règles, vous suivez les règles ou vos héros ? C’est la question qu’on est amené à se poser en voyant le film de Christopher Bell « Bigger, Stronger, Faster ». Ce documentaire poignant au style de Michael Moore, nous plonge dans cette folie des stéroïdes qui touche la famille Bell et plus globalement la nation Américaine tout entière, adepte du “toujours plus”, quel qu’en soit le prix.', 6300, '3.75', 4, 'Documentaire'),
(1204, 'Breakfast with Hunter', '', 'film', 2003, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/85167.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/85167.jpg', 85167, 'tt0367565', 'wD18Q414MS8', 'Breakfast with Hunter is a feature length documentary starring the infamous outlaw journalist Dr. Hunter S. Thompson. Edited by director Wayne Ewing from cinema verite film and digital video that he shot over many years on the road with Dr. Thompson, Breakfast with Hunter follows several story lines in the trials (literally) and triumphs of this cultural icon who created his own genre of writing - Gonzo journalism.', 5460, '0.00', 0, 'Documentaire'),
(1205, 'Breakfast With Jonny Wilkinson', '', 'film', 2013, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/21038.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/21038.jpg', 21038, 'tt3198544', 'null', 'Greyhawks Rugby Club is under threat from land developers, and Dave\'s position as chairman is being challenged by an extremely loud Australian. The faithful few have gathered on the morning before the election to watch England in the Rugby World Cup Final and tensions are running high for more reasons than one Why does Jake, the first team prodigy, leave the room every time Jonny Wilkinson takes a kick?', 0, '3.00', 1, 'Comédie'),
(1206, 'クレヨンしんちゃん 爆睡！ユメミーワールド大突撃', '', 'film', 2016, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/75820.jpg', '', 75820, 'tt5526456', 'null', 'One night, the Nohara family were enjoying a pleasant dream, when suddenly a big fish appeared in their dreams and ate them. The next morning, Hiroshi read in the newspaper that everybody in another town had the same nightmare as him, but it seemed to have ended. But Hiroshi also heard the same dream from Misae, Shinnosuke, Himawari and even Shiro. They were surprised and thought if the same thing is happening in Kasukabe too. In kindergarten, on telling others about his nightmare, Shinnosuke was surprised to know that everybody too had the same dream. Then a mysterious girl named Saki was transferred to Futaba Kindergarten and joined Shinnosuke\'s class. Everyone in the class, including the rather inactive Bo-chan, were all excited and happy on seeing her. But Saki had a cold attitude and didn\'t get along well.', 5820, '0.00', 0, 'Aventure,Animation,Comédie,Familial,Fantastique'),
(1207, 'Full English Breakfast', '', 'film', 2014, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/36194.jpg', '', 36194, 'tt3477732', 'bhmlUiwiq4w', 'Through flashbacks, Full English Breakfast follows the violent career of Dave Bishop (Dave Courtney) a small-time London villain who kills his way to the top of Britain\'s drugs empire. Now happily \'retired\' on the Kent coast Dave becomes embroiled in a bloody battle of wits with Al Qaeda terrorists who want to take over his criminal empire. Adding to the old mobster\'s woes is his younger trophy wife (Lucy Drive) wanting to play away with his new driver (Jamie Bannerman).', 9540, '2.00', 1, 'Action,Crime,Mystère,Thriller'),
(1208, 'Hard, Fast and Beautiful', 'Jeu, set et match', 'film', 1951, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/90891.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/90891.jpg', 90891, 'tt0043619', 'g396gJPmQXk', 'Florence Farley, une adolescente californienne moyenne, accepte une invitation à un country club exclusif de la part du beau Gordon McKay. Lorsque les compétences de Florence en tant que joueuse de tennis commencent à attirer l\'attention, sa mère manipulatrice, Milly la presse de rejoindre le circuit de tennis compétitif pour femmes malgré les réticences de son mari plus modeste.', 4500, '3.00', 1, 'Drame'),
(1209, '我吃了那男孩一整年的早餐', '', 'film', 2022, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/96709.jpg', '', 96709, 'tt17292614', 'iWSjBna8fUA', 'Xiang Wei Xin, a 17-year-old high school sophomore, regards eating as the most important and most healing thing in life. The first time she met her senior Tao You Quan was in the school’s welfare agency. At that time, Xiang Wei Xin lost 5 yuan and could not buy her favorite pineapple bread. Tao You Quan made up the money for her, which made her feel deeply indebted to her. The next day, she saw a breakup scene by the school’s swimming pool. She broke up with her cheating girlfriend but couldn’t separate it. Xiang Wei moved her heart and used her best friend Fang Qi Ran as an excuse to let Tao You Quan break up successfully. She believed that she was brave and repaid.', 7140, '0.00', 0, 'Romance,Drame'),
(1210, 'Nice Girls Don\'t Stay for Breakfast', '', 'film', 2019, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/68147.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/68147.jpg', 68147, 'tt8884452', 'FZPMskK0mvo', 'Bob Mitchum est arrivé au Beverly Hills Hotel le 21 février 1991, pile à l’heure, et s’est mis à chanter l’une de ses chansons préférées de Cole Porter. Il a commencé à nous raconter des histoires de tournages, de bagarres dans les bars, de femmes... L’histoire du cinéma à Hollywood du début des années 40 à 1997 se déroulait sous nos yeux à mesure qu’il racontait ses frasques les plus folles.\" - Bruce Weber', 5400, '3.00', 1, 'Documentaire'),
(1211, 'Phineas and Ferb: The Fast and the Phineas', '', 'film', 2008, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/76638.jpg', '', 76638, '', 'null', 'From the smash-hit Disney Channel Original Series Phineas and Ferb comes The Fast and the Phineas, five hilarious episodes filled with awesome adventures!', 7200, '4.50', 4, ''),
(1212, 'Sex and Breakfast', '', 'film', 2007, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/33025.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/33025.jpg', 33025, 'tt0837803', 'CGFraxRBnBs', 'Two young couples using anonymous sex as a catalyst to fix their troubled relationships must rethink what makes a connection work.', 4860, '2.50', 4, 'Comédie,Drame,Romance'),
(1213, '劇場版新幹線変形ロボシンカリオン 未来からきた神速のALFA-X', '', 'film', 2019, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/106903.jpg', '', 106903, 'tt11628620', 'null', 'The new enemies, Nahane and Ohanefu, along with the mysterious new Giant Monstrous Beings appear from space to take over the Earth! Holding the key to these events is Shinkalion ALFA-X, which was secretly developed by the Ultra Evolution Institute...!? For Hayato and Team Shinkalion, who had been living in peace, the battle begins again.', 4740, '0.00', 0, 'Animation,Action,Aventure,Science-fiction'),
(1214, 'So Much So Fast', '', 'film', 2006, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/44316.jpg', '', 44316, 'tt0492488', 'null', 'A man suffering from Lou Gehrig\'s disease deals with the woman falling for him and a brother who becomes obsessed with finding a cure.', 0, '5.00', 1, 'Documentaire'),
(1215, 'The Last of the Fast Guns', 'Duel dans la Sierra', 'film', 1958, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/79356.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/79356.jpg', 79356, 'tt0051846', 'null', 'Mexique, 1880. Forbes, un riche notable engage Brad Ellison, tueur en quête de reconversion, pour retrouver son frère Edward à qui il souhaite léguer son entreprise à la place de son associé. En route, Brad fait la connaissance de Miles, contremaître du riche O’Reilly avec lequel il poursuit sa recherche, notamment auprès du Padre Jose. Mais l’associé de Forbes ne l’entend pas de cette oreille...', 4920, '0.00', 0, 'Western'),
(1216, 'The Little Cars 6: Fast Lane Fury', '', 'film', 2011, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/114480.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/114480.jpg', 114480, 'tt4793326', 'null', 'Join the Little Cars as they take you on another exciting, speed-racing experience. This is the 6th movie in the series.', 3000, '0.00', 0, 'Téléfilm,Animation,Familial'),
(1217, 'Three for Breakfast', 'Le Petit Déjeuner Est Servi', 'film', 1948, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/99351.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/99351.jpg', 99351, 'tt0040878', 'null', 'C\'est le matin, Tic et Tac se réveillent encore sur leurs noisettes. Comme ils ont élu domicile dans la cheminée de la cuisine de Donald, ils peuvent sentir les délicieux cookies que celui-ci est en train de préparer...', 360, '0.00', 0, 'Animation'),
