(1282, 'Who\'s That Knocking at My Door', '', 'film', 1967, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/15984.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/15984.jpg', 15984, 'tt0063803', '2Yk_oZN7Ux8', 'Petite frappe du quartier italien de New York, J.R. décide de se poser pour épouser la femme qu\'il aime. Il apprend que celle-ci a été violée quelque temps plus tôt et il ne peut en supporter l\'idée.', 5400, '3.57', 7, 'Drame,Romance'),
(1283, '그대 이름은 장미', 'Who is Rose ?', 'film', 2019, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/91388.jpg', '', 91388, 'tt10449248', 'null', 'Quand elle avait vingt ans, Jang-mi voulait devenir une idole. Mais elle tomba enceinte et abandonna son rêve. Elle est désormais une mère célibataire d\'âge moyen qui élève sa fille Hyeon-ah, une mère surprotectrice qui ferait tout pour sa fille. Un jour, Jang-mi retrouve Myeong-hwan, son ex-petit ami. Elle est également surprise de revoir Soon-cheol, le père de Hyeon-ah.', 7560, '4.00', 1, 'Comédie'),
(1284, 'Who?', '', 'film', 1974, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/25680.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/25680.jpg', 25680, 'tt0072405', 'null', 'Après un grave accident de voiture, le physicien américain Lucas Martino se réveille dans une clinique d\'Allemagne de l\'Est et découvre que des implants métalliques ont été utilisés pour lui sauver la vie. De retour aux États-Unis, Lucas est intercepté par le FBI qui doute de l\'identité de l\'homme sous le masque de métal.', 5580, '2.50', 2, 'Mystère,Thriller,Science-fiction,Drame'),
(1285, 'Who Are We?', '', 'film', 1974, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/115137.jpg', '', 115137, 'tt0227808', 'null', 'Canadians in search of the national identity will not find it fully fleshed in this film. An animated cartoon, it sees Canadians as pragmatists, adaptable to whatever climate or history place in their way. It is a boisterous, bubbling analysis of the Canadian character and, although it may not answer the question of the title, it does leave the feeling that being Canadian is not so exhausting as one might expect.', 600, '0.00', 0, 'Animation'),
(1286, 'Who are you?', '', 'film', 2020, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/86068.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/86068.jpg', 86068, 'tt12762898', 'eNsH0TAr_nA', 'The story of a writer who, after having great success with his first book, has a disastrous creative block. So much so, that not even pencils want to write for him. In his anguish, a delivery girl arrives at his door and gives him a mysterious box. After inviting her in to have a coffee, they share a pleasant conversation about fame and success. What’s in the box? Nobody knows what inspiration can be wrapped in.', 780, '0.00', 0, 'Animation'),
(1287, 'Who Are You, Charlie Brown?', 'Qui es-tu, Charlie Brown ?', 'film', 2021, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/90127.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/90127.jpg', 90127, 'tt14784858', 'zIAz8EAIDfo', 'Documentaire sur Peanuts et son créateur, Charles M. Schulz. Des fans célèbres, dont Drew Barrymore, Kevin Smith et Al Roker, partagent son influence sur eux, une nouvelle histoire animée trouve Charlie Brown en quête.', 3660, '3.00', 1, 'Documentaire,Animation'),
(1288, 'کی دسته گل به آب داده؟', '', 'film', 1973, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/48069.jpg', '', 48069, 'tt2266771', 'null', 'Mahmoud and his wife Parvin do not have children after eight years of their marriage. Gol Andam - Rajab\'s concubine wife, Mahmoud\'s servant, leaves her baby in front of Mahmoud\'s house...', 5820, '0.00', 0, 'Comédie'),
(1289, 'Who Do I Gotta Kill?', '', 'film', 1994, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/46655.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/46655.jpg', 46655, 'tt0105815', 'v1XXChZlABg', 'A struggling writer takes a job for his mobster uncle in order to obtain first-hand material for a book on conspiracy plots and the JFK assassination.  They often say that a good writer lives what he writes, but what happens when the life that the writer is living could likely get him killed?', 5040, '0.00', 0, 'Comédie,Crime'),
(1290, 'Who Done It?', '', 'film', 1956, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/61058.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/61058.jpg', 61058, 'tt0049951', 'pv3jeK9ZCGo', 'This movie debut for saucy British TV comic Benny Hill has Benny leaving his job as a sweeper after winning some money. He becomes a private detective and investigates a plot to assassinate British scientists.', 5100, '4.00', 1, 'Action,Comédie'),
(1291, 'Who Done It?', '', 'film', 1949, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/61059.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/61059.jpg', 61059, 'tt0042042', 'null', 'The stooges are private detectives looking for a missing millionaire. They wander around the millionaire\'s spooky mansion confronting various crooks and a dangerous dame. The stooges vanquish the crooks (Shemp uses his \"trusty shovel\") and find the missing man.', 1020, '0.00', 0, 'Comédie'),
(1292, 'Who Done It?', 'Deux nigauds détectives', 'film', 1942, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/56481.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/56481.jpg', 56481, 'tt0035555', '_yILcvT6RC4', 'Deux loosers rêvent de devenir auteurs de polars, notamment pour des feuilletons radiophoniques. Alors qu\'ils essaient de vendre l\'une de leurs créations à une station de radio, ils vont devoir se transformer en véritables détectives quand le propriétaire de la radio est retrouvé mort…', 4620, '0.00', 0, 'Comédie,Mystère'),
(1293, 'Кто, если не мы', '', 'film', 1998, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/45827.jpg', '', 45827, 'tt0261009', 'null', 'This movie deals with two friends, 13-14 year old boys. One comes from a more or less stable home (although he is growing up with single mom) and another comes from a broken up family. One day the kids break into a store to pretty much have fun and get something to eat, short time after they get caught and one kid is sent to juvenile prison (14 year old) and another one is released to his being too young to be tried (13 years old). The younger kid feels bad about such decision, feels guilty and tries to help his friend in any way possible. While trying to help he is meeting a guy, who is ex-cop and now down-on-his-luck drunk(played by Priyomykhov himself)... the two become friends. In the finale, the ex-cop has to go one of the PTA meeting at school (his mother could not get away from work and knows nothing about the ex-cop) where suddenly his mother appears and meets the \"father\"...', 5340, '0.00', 0, 'Drame,Familial'),
(1294, 'Кто придумал колесо?', '', 'film', 1966, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/54829.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/54829.jpg', 54829, 'tt0151263', 'ZXQPv4YZrnQ', 'Окончив школу, Сева Лосев устраивается на химкомбинат. Лирический фильм о первых опытах самостоятельной жизни и первой любви.', 0, '0.00', 0, 'Romance'),
(1295, 'Who Invited Them', '', 'film', 2022, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/110106.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/110106.jpg', 110106, 'tt17677178', 'Tgavhhzfsg8', 'Adam and Margo\'s housewarming party goes well enough except there\'s this one mysterious couple lingering after the other guests have left.', 4800, '0.00', 0, 'Thriller,Horreur'),
