(1297, 'Who Is Cletis Tout?', '', 'film', 2001, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/56339.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/56339.jpg', 56339, 'tt0246500', 'null', 'A comedy about a hitman who sees everything in terms of the movies and how mistaken identity is getting in the way of recovering a stash of diamonds that was stolen and subsequently hidden more than 20 years earlier.', 5520, '0.00', 0, 'Action,Comédie,Crime'),
(1298, 'Who Is Ghislaine Maxwell?', '', 'film', 2022, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/106501.jpg', '', 106501, 'tt4073254', 'null', 'Follows the life of Ghislaine Maxwell, from her early days to meeting convicted sex offender Jeffrey Epstein.', 9060, '3.00', 1, 'Documentaire'),
(1299, 'Who Is Killing the Great Chefs of Europe?', 'La Grande Cuisine', 'film', 1978, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/79908.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/79908.jpg', 79908, 'tt0078488', '05YIFRMKI0o', 'Un par un, les plus grands chefs cuisiniers sont assassinés. Le meurtrier possède une méthode bien particulière : il tue chaque cuisinier de la manière dont celui-ci prépare son meilleur plat.', 6720, '3.40', 5, 'Comédie,Thriller,Mystère'),
(1300, 'Who is KK Downey', '', 'film', 2008, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/45976.jpg', '', 45976, 'tt0944849', 'null', 'The plot revolves around two hipster friends who pretend to be a writer with a troubled past in their quest for fame.', 5400, '3.00', 1, 'Comédie,Romance'),
(1301, 'Who Is Simon Miller?', '', 'film', 2011, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/40003.jpg', '', 40003, 'tt1928242', 'null', 'Like most families, the Millers have their challenges. Simon\'s frequent business trips have created some distance between him and the rest of the family, leaving Meredith stretched and struggling to keep things together. Daughter Sarah, an 18-year-old honor student, has recently gotten herself into trouble at school while son Kevin, 15, struggles to engage with anything outside of a video game... But these issues all prove to be trivial when Simon goes missing...', 5100, '0.00', 0, 'Familial,Téléfilm'),
(1302, 'Кто первый?', '', 'film', 1950, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/113483.jpg', '', 113483, 'tt6118508', 'null', 'The animation film in comic form shows the sporting struggle in the bicycle race between the forest animals: the Toptygin brothers, the Bunny and the Fox. After a long, exhausting struggle, the Bunny took the lead, however, prematurely fed up with the victory, shamefully loses the match: after detachment from the opponents the Bunny decides to rest lying under a tree , then bathes (right in the bicycle form - a T-shirt and shorts), forgets to control the time and loses the championship in the race.', 600, '0.00', 0, 'Animation,Familial'),
(1303, 'Хто в лісі хазяїн?', '', 'film', 1977, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/116016.jpg', '', 116016, '', 'null', 'Many animals live in the forest. They all have their own characters and ambitions, the relationship between themselves and the settled way of life. One day a Bear decided to prove to everyone that he is the most important one. How will animals perceive such brazen statements? Will they be frightened and obey or put the high-handed insolent in his place?', 480, '0.00', 0, 'Animation'),
(1304, '谁的本领大', '', 'film', 1961, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/114024.jpg', '', 114024, '', 'null', 'The magpie asked who had the greatest ability, and the deer jumped out and said it was it because it ran fast. The little monkey didn\'t take it seriously, saying that it was the most capable because it could climb trees. The little deer and the little monkey couldn\'t stop arguing, and asked the magpie to comment, but the magpie scratched his head and gave it to Uncle Xiong. Uncle Xiong said that the game will tell the difference, so the little deer and the little monkey competed to pick peaches on the other side of the river.', 600, '0.00', 0, 'Animation'),
(1305, 'Who Killed Bill?', '', 'film', 2010, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/107584.jpg', '', 107584, '', 'null', 'Johnny Rotten, Sid Vicious and The Sex Pistols, iconic names that conjure up all that s bad in rock and roll. Since the historic Bill Grundy interview that shocked a nation, The Sex Pistols have constantly been in the news, whether gaining good or bad press, it all adds to the bad boy image of the worlds most outrageous band. Charting their explosive TV exploits from 1976 to the present day including the split and reforming of the band and the death of Sid Vicious, this revealing documentary showcases rare and forgotten archive of the world s most notorious punk rockers.', 7200, '0.00', 0, ''),
(1306, 'Who Killed Billie-Jo', '', 'film', 2022, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/120198.jpg', '', 120198, '', 'null', 'Examen du cas du meurtre de Billie-Jo Jenkins, treize ans, sur la terrasse de sa maison le 15 février 1997. Des experts témoignent, convaincus en nombre égal que les preuves médico-légales incriminent ou disculpent son père adoptif.', 5640, '0.00', 0, 'Documentaire'),
(1307, 'Who Killed Captain Alex?', '', 'film', 2010, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/50504.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/50504.jpg', 50504, 'tt1813757', 'BymeLkZ7GqM', 'Reconnu comme le premier film d\'action ougandais, Who Killed Captain Alex ? parle des conséquences d\'une descente de police à Kampala au cours de laquelle un capitaine de police est tué.', 4080, '3.50', 2, 'Action,Drame,Comédie'),
(1308, 'Who Killed Cock Robin?', 'Qui a Tué le Rouge-Gorge ?', 'film', 1935, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/98582.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/98582.jpg', 98582, 'tt0027212', 'null', 'Le chanteur Rouge-Gorge faisait une sérénade à Jenny Wren, une sémillante femelle, au moment où il se fait tuer par une flèche. Débute alors une enquête policière et un procès. Trois coupables comparaissent à la barre : Black Bird (un merle noir), Legs Sparrow (un moineau) et Cuckoo (un coucou).', 540, '0.00', 0, 'Familial,Animation,Comédie,Crime'),
(1309, '目擊者', '', 'film', 2017, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/54255.jpg', '', 54255, 'tt5576318', 'oNP4ljNZzWw', 'An ambitious journalist who witnessed a hit-and-run years ago reboots his investigation led by newly emerged clues. As he beats the clock to save the only survivor after her sudden disappearance, layers of unimaginable dark truths around a corrupted system start peeling.', 7080, '4.00', 1, 'Mystère,Thriller,Crime'),
(1310, 'Who Killed Cooper Dunn?', '', 'film', 2022, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/118953.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/118953.jpg', 118953, 'tt12960310', 'wozOAfS2z68', 'Six lifelong friends embark on a camping trip. When one of them ends up dead, loyalties are tested as they try to find who\'s responsible.', 5400, '0.00', 0, 'Mystère'),
(1311, 'Who Killed Gail Preston?', '', 'film', 1938, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/107707.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/107707.jpg', 107707, 'tt0030974', 'null', 'A temperamental singer\'s murder leaves a nightclub full of suspects.', 3660, '0.00', 0, 'Crime,Drame,Mystère,Romance'),
(1312, 'Who Killed JonBenét?', 'Qui a tué la petite JonBenét ?', 'film', 2016, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/59129.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/59129.jpg', 59129, 'tt6267670', 'RE9k0e-zu-s', 'Une reine de beauté de six ans est retrouvée morte dans le sous-sol de la maison familiale. Les parents de la fillette évoquent un enlèvement. Une demande de rançon est formulée, corroborant cette version. Mais très vite, la victime est retrouvée, dans la cave, le crâne fracassé, un cordon autour du cou...', 4800, '4.13', 8, 'Crime,Téléfilm'),
(1313, 'Who Killed Lady Winsley', 'Qui a tué Lady Winsley ?', 'film', 2019, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/67018.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/67018.jpg', 67018, 'tt7035302', 'K8XiOsbQxuQ', 'Lady Winsley, une romancière américaine, est assassinée sur une petite île turque. Le célèbre inspecteur Fergün arrive d’Istanbul pour mener l’enquête. Très vite, il doit alors faire face à des secrets bien gardés dans ce petit coin de pays où les tabous sont nombreux, les liens familiaux étroits, les traditions ancestrales et la diversité ethnique plus large que les esprits.', 5400, '2.95', 21, 'Crime,Comédie'),
(1314, 'Who Killed My Husband', 'Une femme contre le crime', 'film', 2016, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/59141.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/59141.jpg', 59141, 'tt4833952', 'null', 'Une policière est plongée dans une lutte à mort contre le crime organisé.', 6300, '0.00', 0, 'Téléfilm,Thriller,Mystère,Crime'),
(1315, 'Who Killed My Son?', '', 'film', 2021, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/99994.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/99994.jpg', 99994, 'tt14170460', 'null', 'In the colder time of year of 2014, an Indian American understudy named Pravin Varughese disappears in the little, southern Illinois city of Carbondale. Close to 7 days after Pravin’s vanishing, his body is found and the specialists rule his demise a mishap.', 5100, '0.00', 0, 'Documentaire'),
(1316, 'Who Killed the Co-ed?: An ID Murder Mystery', '', 'film', 2020, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/95276.jpg', '', 95276, 'tt12413302', 'null', 'When 19-year-old college student Faith Hedgepeth is found brutally murdered in her off campus apartment, the evidence leads police to believe that she knew her killer. Six years later Faith\'s murderer is still at large. Who killed Faith?', 2520, '0.00', 0, ''),
(1317, 'Who Killed the Lyon Sisters?', '', 'film', 2020, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/94903.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/94903.jpg', 94903, 'tt13370308', 'null', 'Sisters Katherine and Sheila Lyon vanish from a Wheaton, Maryland mall in 1975, launching a 40-year search for the girls. This case was one of the largest police investigations in the history of the Washington, DC metropolitan area.', 0, '0.00', 0, ''),
(1318, 'Who Killed Vincent Chin?', '', 'film', 1987, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/97417.jpg', '', 97417, 'tt0096440', 'null', 'This film recounts the murder of Vincent Chin, an automotive engineer mistaken as Japanese who was slain by an assembly line worker who blamed him for the competition by the Japanese auto makers that were threatening his job. It then recounts how that murderer escaped justice in the court system.  Restored by the Academy Film Archive and The Film Foundation, in association with the Museum of Chinese in America. Restoration funding provided by the Hobson/Lucas Family Foundation, with additional support provided by Todd Phillips.', 5220, '0.00', 0, 'Documentaire,Crime,Histoire');
