(1409, 'ドクター秩父山', '', 'film', 1988, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/36782.jpg', '', 36782, '', 'null', 'Dr. Chichibuyama is the perverse head of a hospital way out in the mountains and terrorises patients with the help of his lover and a sexy young nurse.', 1800, '0.00', 0, 'Comédie'),
(1410, 'Doctor Detroit', '', 'film', 1983, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/75031.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/75031.jpg', 75031, 'tt0085450', 'KNf9gCzJrbw', 'Un homme timide mais doux du nom de Clifford Skridlow est professeur de littérature comparée au Monroe College de Chicago, en difficulté financière. Une rencontre fortuite avec quatre belles femmes dans un restaurant change sa vie pour toujours.', 5340, '3.00', 1, 'Comédie'),
(1411, 'Doctor Dolittle', 'L\'Extravagant Docteur Dolittle', 'film', 1967, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/24448.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/24448.jpg', 24448, 'tt0061584', '49CmzIRX1k0', 'Un petit port de pêche d\'Angleterre, en 1845. Le vétérinaire du village, John Dolittle, passionné d\'animaux, a appris le langage de nombre d\'entre eux grâce à son perroquet. Il ne recherche pas la compagnie des humains qui le prennent pour un fou. Ayant reçu, en cadeau d\'un ami, un lama à deux têtes \"Tire-moi, Pousse-moi\", il le vend à Albert Blossom, directeur de cirque, pour financer son voyage à la recherche de l\'Escargot des Mers. Mais bientôt, il est arrêté et condamné à l\'internement par le Juge de Paix, le général Bellowes, pour ses \"extravagances\". Avec la complicité de Matthew Mug, Tommy Stubbins et Emma Fairfax (nièce du général), il s\'évade et prend la mer avec eux. Un naufrage les jette sur le rivage de \"l’Ile sous les étoiles\", une île flottante en danger : les courants la poussent vers le nord.', 9120, '4.00', 5, 'Comédie,Familial,Fantastique'),
(1412, 'Doctor Doom', '', 'film', 0, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/68027.jpg', '', 68027, 'tt7164792', 'null', 'Marvel\'s Doctor Doom tells the origin story of Victor Von Doom and how he becomes the infamous Dr. Doom.', 0, '0.00', 0, 'Thriller,Science-fiction,Drame'),
(1413, 'Doctor in Clover', '', 'film', 1966, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/46441.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/46441.jpg', 46441, 'tt0060321', 'null', 'Doctor in Clover is another \'Doctor\' movie, but this time Leslie Phillips is the main doctor in the story, looking for love and romance from the hospital nurses, much to the annoyance of the main Administrator (James Robertson Justice) who wants his doctors to be 100% focussed on the job. Numerous antics follow, with Phillips getting Justice fixed up with the new prim-and-proper Matron (Joan Sims) and his attempted failures to lure the hospital\'s beauty, the physiotherapist.', 5820, '3.00', 1, 'Comédie'),
(1414, 'Doctor in the House', 'Toubib or not Toubib', 'film', 1954, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/111500.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/111500.jpg', 111500, 'tt0046921', 'null', 'Simon Sparrow est un étudiant en médecine fraîchement débarqué à l\'hôpital St Swithin de Londres. Placé dans le même rang que trois ambitieux plus expérimentés que lui, il se trouve bientôt plongé dans l\'entraînement médical tel qu\'il se concevait dans les années 1950, un entraînement constitué par la drague, la consommation d’alcool et la conduite rapide de voitures de sport ! Mais Sir Lancelot Spratt, le médecin chef, veille, et est toujours là pour les rappeler à l’ordre…', 5520, '0.00', 0, 'Comédie'),
(1415, '닥터 K', '', 'film', 1999, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/33855.jpg', '', 33855, 'tt0239349', 'null', 'Terminally ill patients are magically cured by a neurosurgeon who transfers their tumors to his own brain.', 6420, '0.00', 0, 'Romance,Drame,Fantastique'),
(1416, 'Doctor Lollipop', '', 'film', 2013, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/30897.jpg', '', 30897, 'tt2782742', 'null', 'Two words: Unicorn. Physician', 360, '4.00', 1, 'Comédie,Animation'),
(1417, 'Doctor Mordrid', 'Docteur Mordrid', 'film', 1992, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/75030.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/75030.jpg', 75030, 'tt0104115', 'M-BjMiezgxs', 'Un mal indicible est venu dans notre dimension et veut régner sur la Terre, et seul un mystérieux sorcier connu sous le nom de docteur Mordrid peut l\'arrêter.', 3720, '2.00', 1, 'Fantastique,Action,Thriller,Science-fiction,Horreur'),
(1418, 'Doctor of Doom', '', 'film', 1979, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/23443.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/23443.jpg', 23443, 'tt0898907', 'null', 'Un médecin se rend à un diner, mais les invités se moquent de lui.  Une fois rentré chez lui, il crée un monstre pour se venger.', 660, '2.00', 2, 'Horreur,Comédie'),
(1419, 'Doctor Oswald', '', 'film', 1935, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/104334.jpg', '', 104334, 'tt0142226', 'null', 'An Oswald the Lucky Rabbit cartoon.', 0, '0.00', 0, 'Animation'),
(1420, 'Doctor Satán', '', 'film', 1966, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/44572.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/44572.jpg', 44572, 'tt0178391', 'null', 'Dr. Satan, a mad scientist and sorceror, plans to take over the world. In order to do so, he wakes up three zombie slaves from the dead and attempts to make a deal with the devil. He sends his zombie servants to do harm to anyone who stands in his way. Will anyone be able to stop him?', 5520, '3.00', 1, 'Horreur'),
(1421, 'Доктор Свисток', '', 'film', 2022, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/94102.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/94102.jpg', 94102, '', '0Xw-5ImMIoY', 'Arsen from the seaside Dagomys dreamed of becoming a plastic surgeon since childhood. His dream almost came true - he got a job in a Moscow plastic surgery clinic... as an administrator. Arsen did not have a medical education, but he was good at earning money by passing off Chinese implants for Swiss ones or selling a place in a queue to patients. Everything was seized from him, until the \"fresh tuning\" of the next star of show business exploded right on board the plane! Together with fake implants, Arsen\'s career was scattered to shreds - he was forced to flee from Moscow to his native Sochi. Where, in what he is sure, his rich experience will allow him to open his own clinic and make this world a better place! Well, or at least more.', 5580, '0.00', 0, 'Comédie'),
(1422, 'Doctor Who Am I', '', 'film', 2022, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/118985.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/118985.jpg', 118985, 'tt12029866', 'hZDT-txBQgw', 'In 1996, a Doctor Who TV movie was envisioned to lead the franchise into an exciting new future with a fresh direction but was met only by an outcry from disapproving fans. Now, follow the film’s screenwriter, Matthew Jacobs, as he is pulled back into the world of the Doctor Who fandom, where he unexpectedly finds himself a kindred part of this close-knit, yet vast, family of fans.', 4800, '0.00', 0, 'Documentaire'),
(1423, 'Doctor Who: Attack of the Cybermen', '', 'film', 1985, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/109037.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/109037.jpg', 109037, '', 'null', 'An alien distress call draws the Doctor and Peri to Earth, 1985, where they uncover a Cyberman plot to change the course of history.', 5400, '5.00', 1, 'Drame,Action,Aventure,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1424, 'Doctor Who: Battlefield', '', 'film', 1989, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/29868.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/29868.jpg', 29868, '', 'null', 'Knights from a parallel universe arrive on Earth to find the legendary sword Excalibur. Only the Doctor and Ace, with the assistance of Brigadier Lethbridge-Stewart, can save the Earth from total catastrophe.', 5700, '4.00', 2, 'Fantastique,Science-fiction,Téléfilm,Action,Aventure'),
(1425, 'Doctor Who: Castrovalva', '', 'film', 1982, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108982.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108982.jpg', 108982, '', 'null', 'The Doctor needs somewhere peaceful to recover from his traumatic regeneration. But the sanctuary of Castrovalva is not all it seems, as the Master will stop at nothing to gain his revenge over the Doctor...', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Drame,Aventure,Science-fiction,Téléfilm,Action'),
(1426, 'Doctor Who: City of Death', '', 'film', 1979, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/29875.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/29875.jpg', 29875, '', 'nH48k3utGHw', 'While taking in the sights of Paris in 1979, the Doctor and Romana sense that someone is tampering with time. Who is the mysterious Count Scarlioni? Why does he seem to have counterparts scattered through time? And just how many copies of the Mona Lisa did Leonardo da Vinci paint?', 6000, '4.00', 2, 'Comédie,Aventure,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1427, 'Doctor Who: Colony in Space', '', 'film', 1971, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/118125.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/118125.jpg', 118125, '', 'null', 'When the Master steals the Time Lords\' secret file on the Doomsday Weapon, they grant the Doctor a temporary reprieve from his exile on Earth to deal with the crisis. He and Jo arrive on the planet Uxarieus and become enmeshed in a struggle between an agrarian colony and a powerful mining corporation.', 9000, '5.00', 1, 'Science-fiction,Drame,Aventure'),
(1428, 'Doctor Who: Day of the Daleks', '', 'film', 1972, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108853.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108853.jpg', 108853, '', 'null', 'Guerillas time-jump back from the 22nd century to assassinate Sir Reginald Styles - a diplomat working for World Peace, The Doctor discovers they are from a future where the Daleks have invaded the Earth (Following wars precipitated by Styles\'s destruction at the peace conference). With the Daleks desperate to maintain their version of history, The Doctor and Jo find themselves in a totalitarian future, where they must discover who really happened and prevent it.', 5760, '5.00', 1, 'Familial,Aventure,Drame,Téléfilm'),
(1429, 'Doctor Who: Death to the Daleks', '', 'film', 1974, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108865.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108865.jpg', 108865, '', 'null', 'An energy drain traps the Third Doctor and Sarah Jane Smith on the planet Exxilon with its hostile natives, causing the travellers to make an uneasy alliance with a Marine Space Corps expedition and a squadron of Daleks. The key to escape for all of them lies at the heart of a powerful and mysterious lost city, but only after a series of deadly traps.', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Drame,Action,Aventure,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1430, 'Doctor Who: Destiny of the Daleks', '', 'film', 1979, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108916.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108916.jpg', 108916, '', 'ssYORbe73eo', 'The Doctor and a newly-regenerated Romana arrive on Skaro to find that the Daleks, locked in a war with the robotic Movellans, have returned to retrieve their buried creator Davros.', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Action,Aventure,Drame,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1431, 'Doctor Who: Enlightenment', '', 'film', 1983, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108997.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108997.jpg', 108997, '', 'null', 'An Edwardian yacht in deep space races around the planets. There is a double agent in the TARDIS crew. The White Guardian warns the Fifth Doctor of great danger. Turlough must finally choose sides and at the end of the race lies the prize of Enlightenment.', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Drame,Action,Aventure,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1432, 'Doctor Who: Four to Doomsday', '', 'film', 1982, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108983.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108983.jpg', 108983, '', 'null', 'The Doctor and his companions arrive on a spaceship headed for Earth, populated by natives of Earth from various different eras and commanded by the leaders of the Urbankan race. What are the Urbankans\' intentions when they reach Earth?', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Drame,Action,Aventure,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1433, 'Doctor Who: Full Circle', '', 'film', 1980, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108953.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108953.jpg', 108953, '', 'QiW-2GDs1jM', 'On the planet Alzarius in the alternate universe of E-Space, the Doctor, Romana and K9 find survivors of a crashed starliner, strange creatures lurking in the marshes and a genetic riddle which stretches back centuries.', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Action,Aventure,Drame,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1434, 'Doctor Who: Ghost Light', '', 'film', 1989, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/116295.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/116295.jpg', 116295, '', 'null', 'The Doctor takes Ace on an initiative test to a strange Victorian old house where she is forced to confront her darkest fears.', 4500, '5.00', 1, 'Science-fiction,Drame,Aventure'),
(1435, 'Doctor Who: Horror of Fang Rock', '', 'film', 1977, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108877.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108877.jpg', 108877, '', 'null', 'The cursed island of Fang Rock off the south coast of England is a place of rumour and tales of beasts from the sea. Three lighthouse men at the turn of the century face their fears when something comes from the sea to bring death to all it touches.', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Action,Aventure,Drame,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1436, 'Doctor Who: Image of the Fendahl', '', 'film', 1977, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108879.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108879.jpg', 108879, '', 'JYRkEjGRWRY', 'The present day: just as the Fourth Doctor and Leela arrive in Fetchborough, England, Professor Fendelman prepares to experiment on a fossilized skull which science says should not exist. The skull is actually an artefact of the Fendahl, a god-like being who feeds on the life force of others. It has begun to awaken and kill. Worse yet, others seek to exploit the Fendahl\'s dreadful power.', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Action,Aventure,Drame,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1437, 'Doctor Who: Inferno', '', 'film', 1970, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/29870.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/29870.jpg', 29870, '', 'null', 'Inferno is a top-secret project that involves drilling down into the crust of the Earth to unleash a new energy source. However, the Doctor, along with his assistant Liz Shaw, is concerned that this drilling will have disastrous consequences for the whole world.', 10500, '4.00', 2, 'Science-fiction,Drame,Aventure'),
(1438, 'Doctor Who: Kinda', '', 'film', 1982, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108984.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108984.jpg', 108984, '', 'null', 'The TARDIS lands on the idyllic jungle world of Deva Loka, which is being surveyed for possible Earth colonisation. Deva Loka is already home to a race of apparent savages, however: a mysterious people with strange powers which have mentally unbalanced the members of the expedition. To make matters worse, an ancient enemy of the natives known as the Mara is intent upon revenge, and latches onto Tegan\'s mind as its bridgehead to victory.', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Drame,Action,Aventure,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1439, 'Doctor Who Live: The Afterparty', '', 'film', 2013, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/116486.jpg', '', 116486, 'tt3503582', 'null', 'Zoe Ball and Rick Edwards get the party started for the celebration of 50 years of Doctor Who, with Doctors and companions past and present, celebrity fans and special surprises.', 3540, '0.00', 0, ''),
(1440, 'Doctor Who: Marco Polo', '', 'film', 1964, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/104400.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/104400.jpg', 104400, 'tt0562858', 'null', 'The TARDIS crew lands in the Himalayas of Cathay in 1289, their ship badly damaged, and are picked up by Marco Polo\'s caravan on its way along the fabled Silk Road to see the Emperor Kublai Khan. The story concerns the Doctor and his companions\' attempts to thwart the machinations of Tegana, who attempts to sabotage the caravan along its travels through the Pamir Plateau and across the treacherous Gobi Desert, and ultimately to assassinate Kublai Khan in Peking, at the height of his imperial power.', 10500, '5.00', 1, 'Science-fiction,Aventure,Drame'),
(1441, 'Doctor Who: Mawdryn Undead', '', 'film', 1983, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108994.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108994.jpg', 108994, '', 'null', 'A warp ellipse draws the TARDIS off course. The Fifth Doctor\'s companions are separated from him not in space, but in time, and he has to deal with a treacherous schoolboy named Turlough. But why does the Doctor\'s old friend, the Brigadier, not remember him at all?', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Drame,Action,Aventure,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1442, 'Doctor Who: Meglos', '', 'film', 1980, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108950.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108950.jpg', 108950, '', 'null', 'On the lush planet Tigella, two opposing factions are divided over the usage of the Dodecahedron, an ancient and powerful artefact which provides the entire planet\'s energy. The Doctor is summoned to arbitrate the conflict, but the power-crazed Meglos intercepts the call and impersonates him in order to steal the Dodecahedron.', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Action,Aventure,Drame,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1443, 'Doctor Who: Mindwarp', '', 'film', 1986, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/59450.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/59450.jpg', 59450, '', 'null', 'As the Doctor\'s trial continues, evidence is presented showing his most recent adventure, one where he faces an old adversary, Sil. As a scientist conducts his unethical experiments to prolong the life of Sil\'s boss Kiv, the Doctor\'s memories of the events begins to return and an unpleasant surprise awaits him.', 6000, '4.00', 2, 'Science-fiction,Drame,Action,Aventure'),
(1444, 'Doctor Who: Nightmare of Eden', '', 'film', 1979, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108937.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108937.jpg', 108937, '', 'aDG11TJO4kc', 'A freak accident leaves two dangerously unstable spacecraft locked together, and a horde of monsters unleashed on their passengers.', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Action,Aventure,Drame,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1445, 'Doctor Who: Origins', '', 'film', 2006, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/120646.jpg', '', 120646, '', 'null', 'A 55-minute documentary, detailing the creation of Doctor Who, including a rare interview with creator Sydney Newman, and new interviews with producer Verity Lambert, directors Waris Hussein and Richard Martin, actors William Russell and Carole Ann Ford, title sequence designer Bernard Lodge, and TARDIS sound effect creator Brian Hodgson', 3240, '0.00', 0, 'Documentaire'),
(1446, 'Doctor Who: Planet of the Daleks', '', 'film', 1973, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108861.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108861.jpg', 108861, '', 'null', 'On the jungle planet Spiridon, the Doctor, Jo and a Thal group find a slumbering army of Daleks ready to awaken.', 9000, '5.00', 1, 'Drame,Action,Aventure,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1447, 'Doctor Who: Planet of the Spiders', '', 'film', 1974, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108866.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108866.jpg', 108866, '', 'null', 'The blue crystal that the Doctor took from Metebelis III in a previous adventure is desperately sought by the Eight Legs, a race of mutated spiders, as the final element in their plan for universal domination. With help from an old mentor, the Doctor realises the only way to foil the plot is to make the ultimate sacrifice. The Doctor must risk death to return to the cave of the Great One and save the universe.', 9000, '5.00', 1, 'Drame,Action,Aventure,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1448, 'Doctor Who: Rain', '', 'film', 2014, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/29864.jpg', '', 29864, '', 'null', 'A stylised, narrative short film made in anticipation of the 8th series of Doctor Who.', 60, '0.00', 0, 'Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1449, 'Doctor Who: Revelation of the Daleks', '', 'film', 1985, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/109041.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/109041.jpg', 109041, '', 'null', 'At the Tranquil Repose mortuary, the Doctor and Peri uncover a sinister plot to create a new breed of Daleks under the supervision of the mysterious Great Healer.', 5400, '5.00', 1, 'Drame,Action,Aventure,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1450, 'Doctor Who: Revenge of the Cybermen', '', 'film', 1975, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108870.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108870.jpg', 108870, 'tt0562874', 's9nJU7hpzYY', 'Arriving on Space Station Nerva in its distant past, the Doctor, Sarah and Harry find its crew threatened by a mysterious plague. Discovering that things are not as they seem, they uncover a Cyberman plot to destroy Voga, planet of gold.', 6000, '5.00', 1, 'Action,Aventure,Drame,Science-fiction,Téléfilm'),
(1451, 'Doctor Who: Robot', '', 'film', 1975, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/108952.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/108952.jpg', 108952, 'tt0562875', 'GM8RT_cp0RE', 'The newly-regenerated Doctor helps UNIT battle a sentient robot being manipulated by a corrupt scientific organization.', 5880, '5.00', 1, 'Science-fiction,Aventure,Drame'),
