(1498, 'Bodyguard Seduction', '', 'film', 2022, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/113690.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/113690.jpg', 113690, 'tt21292180', 'null', 'Charly, a wealthy business woman, must decide whom she can trust when she falls for a sexy bodyguard who might be involved in a plot to assassinate her. Charly relies on seduction to get to the truth when her life is threatened more than once by a mysterious killer. Who could it be? What\'s their agenda? Will Charly find out before it\'s too late?', 5400, '0.00', 0, 'Thriller,Mystère,Téléfilm'),
(1499, '十月圍城', 'Bodyguards et Assassins', 'film', 2009, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/12361.jpg', 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/backdrops/original/12361.jpg', 12361, 'tt1403130', 'Kf1l4KapO6I', 'Hong Kong, 1906, à la fin des Qing, Sun Yat-sen, leader nationaliste et républicain en exil au Japon, doit se rendre dans la colonie britannique pour rencontrer les chefs révolutionnaires de différentes provinces. La cour impériale chinoise saisit l\'occasion pour envoyer un régiment d\'assassins... Chez les partisans du père de la Chine moderne, on s\'organise.', 8280, '3.76', 17, 'Drame,Action,Histoire'),
(1500, '修羅の黙示録2 ボディーガード牙', '', 'film', 1995, 'https://pictures.betaseries.com/films/affiches/original/93145.jpg', '', 93145, 'tt0303784', 'null', 'When a young karate student attempts to earn some extra cash by serving as bodyguard to a high-profile Hong Kong woman, the initial distraction of her beauty soon gives way to razor sharp focus as a series of attackers descend upon the pair.', 4440, '0.00', 0, 'Action');
